        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> Hello all.<BR>I'm looking for upgrade advice for a 44 Iksar Necro.  His int is 169 and hp, buffed with arch shielding, is 1060.  I've read a lot about hp>int, but I'm wondering how low I should let int go.  For instance, trading out a batskull earring for one of the hp & mana ones.<BR>  I currently only have around 2500 to spend, but I'm in farm mode, so I'm looking for stuff to shoot for.  Gear is listed below, hardly uber, but he earned it all himself.</P><P>Thanks,<BR>Suttig<BR>Level 44 necro of Bertoxx</P><P>Revenant Skullcap<BR>Bat Skull Earring<BR>Golden Black Sapphire Earring<BR>Sheer Bone Mask<BR>Petrified Erudite Heart Amulet<BR>Frozen Mantle<BR>Gatorscale Sleeves<BR>Shadow Bound Gloves<BR>Bracelet of Woven Grass<BR>4 ac 45 hp ring<BR>5 ac 55 hp ring<BR>Green Silken Drape<BR>Cloak of the Forlorn<BR>Spider Fur Belt<BR>Gatorscale Leggings<BR>Shadow Bound Boots<BR>Post Nerf CoS<BR>Stein of Moggok<BR>Tome of the Eternal</P><P></P><P><BR> </font></td>

