        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Many options out there, for starters try</P><P>Coterie General Cape AC8 STR5 INT4 HP40 (500-1k)<BR>Elder Wolf Hide AC10 STR4 WIS4 INT4 HP30 (1-1.5k)<BR>Crystal Spider Eyes AC8 WIS3 INT3 HP35 MANA35 (500-1k)<BR>Spider Fur Boots AC6 CHA5 HP45 (250-400)</P><P>Those price ranges are what I've seen on Luclin server, obviously yours may differ. On a good day you might find all within your budget of 2500.</P><P>Go through the magelo profiles of people on the boards in the 45-55 range and you'll find often there are "standard" items that typically everyone is wearing, that will give you a better idea of what to aim for</P><P></P><P>Narben the Gnome Gnecro<BR>Colleague of Sanctuary<BR>Luclin server<BR>"Find your own damn witty comment"<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
