        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Ilt:  I gotta disagree with you man.  The reason we have HP is NOT to withstand nukes.  Its to siphon away with our HP-MANA spells.  We want HP to get MANA as FAST as possible.  </P><P>So YES we take a few nukes, we drain it back and kill the mob faster than if we just had INT MANA gear.  </P><P>So having a HUGE mana pool is great...until it runs out. If you have HP gear, you can Lich away your hp and get mana back FAST.  "It's not the SIZE of the tank (mana), but how FAST you can fill it up (hp/mana spell)."</P><P><strong>Deedrok - Level 45<BR>  Necromancer of E'ci<BR>  <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234678" target="_blank">My Gear</a></strong><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
