        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         My profile at 45 is below.  I've been doing some upgrades lately might give you some ideas.  While hollowshade is in its virgin state from the patch go camp yourself an elder wolf hide.  I did this 2 nights ago.  Great shoulder piece.  </P><P>Run in the wolf cave invis find the packleader or ghowlik if he's up and get behind him in the corner.  Cast dark on him and reinvis (CoS if you have one) run out of the cave and root rot once he comes out.  You could probably just channel a VoS and some dd's and do ok too.  Once he's dead make a pet and set up camp behind the spawn.  Boner can solo these guys no sweat I would usually channel a dark (to prevent running) and FD and let boner kill'm.  From the corner you'll have 1 roamer and your named spawn to worry about.  Super easy.  Took me 3 hours and 5 ghowliks to get the hide.  GL.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=119694" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=119694</a></P><P>X</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
