        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Just keep in mind that having more hps does not make you generate mana any faster.  Getting mana at 13 per tick or whatever doesn't change with more hps, it just means you can go longer before liching it back.</P><P>I think HPs are a good idea, as long as you understand the result.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
