         Guy I'm at work atm but I will post what gear and stats I have.<BR>This is from memory so I'll post again.</P><P>INT 217<BR>WIS 113<BR>HP  1158  (Unbuffed)</P><P>Not sure on resist but atm I carry a full set of BD gear for those caster types hehe.</P><P>Right now I know that I and wearing  Two Diamond rings, One Blue Diamond Earring, One Blue Diamond Neck.  So my resists are good without 4 of my other Diamond/Blue Diamond gear on.</P><P>BUT!  I will have to say I would go with HP gear because it doesn't matter what your fighting if you get hit more than a few times your toast.  Even if you resist most of the spell 3 or 4 500 AE spells hitting for part of the dmg will kill you.  With no gear on I think i have 890 hp but I'll repost.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
